    leaf filterDelay {
      description "Reduces toggling alarm notifications by configuring delay before an alarm is cleared. Subsequent alarm port state changes to active state occurring during this time are reported as one alarm event. Exact time of clearing the alarm is chosen by the system, but not lower than value set.; range 60..28800; Default value: 60.";
